<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/507099-sorry-my-question-might-me-kind-of">Sorry, my question might me kind of obvious but I&#39;m new in &#39;goodreads&#39;.
Can I read &#39;Ruin: The Waking&#39; (online or downloaded) on a computer or do I have to have a kindle?
And if I can read it on the computer, where do I click to start reading?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
