<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/8033336-jonathan"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
