<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/8033336-jonathan">Jonathan</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">You can download Kindle for PC and use your computer to read Kindle books. Similarly, Barnes and Nobles has the Nook software to read their ebooks on <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">You can download Kindle for PC and use your computer to read Kindle books. Similarly, Barnes and Nobles has the Nook software to read their ebooks on computer.<br /><br />Here is the link for Kindle for PC:<br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=help_search_1-1?ie=UTF8&amp;nodeId=201245960&amp;qid=1442722784&amp;sr=1-1">http://www.amazon.com/gp/help/custome...</a><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
